snippet.title: Tail Concerto Trailer 1999
snippet.description:
Tail Concerto Trailer 1999

Official Content From Atlus

Take on the role of the heroic policeman Waffle. It's up to you to protect the floating Islands of Prairie form the Black Cats Gang. Use your mech-suit to run, fly, shoot, climb, jump your way through 8 exciting lands filled with dangerous obstacles.
Platforms: Sony PlayStation

Sony PlayStation
